<ab facs="#facs_469_r2l8">habt / Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>v̈lr<ex>ich</ex></expan> heͣrlın vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_469_r2l9"><expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kıſtn<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / Den wır befolhen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt eẅch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒureden </ab>
