</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_469" id="233v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir den
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> bey ewch auf ein urfee ledig
                                <expan>gelass<ex>en</ex></expan> und den
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> etwas gemeͣrt habt, also
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>Ülr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Heͣrlin und <expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Kistn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, den wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ewch <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>ben</expan>, daz ir
                        in das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und ewch darinn so willig
                        und <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
